-- Toyota Can’t Compel Arbitration in Prius Brake Cases
-- B y   K a r e n   G u l l o
-- 2013-01-30T18:17:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-30/toyota-can-t-compel-arbitration-in-prius-brake-cases.html
Toyota Motor Corp. (7203)  can’t force Prius
owners into arbibration related to the performance of the car’s
brakes, a U.S. appeals court said in upholding a lower-court
ruling.  To contact the reporter on this story:
